The museum of Cham sculptures
Aug 2016 • Couples
The museum is located on the banks of the Han River in Da Nang. It has on display the sculptures collected from various Cham sites eg. My Son,Tra Kieu, Dong Duong and several other sites. The sculptures depict Hindu Gods and some of them are still in fine shape. Its a place visited by many tourists.
