3.0 of 5 bubbles
Facilities needs updating
Jul 2016
This is such an important place for Da Nang in terms of its cultural heritage. I went here and could not stay for longer than a few minutes because of the heat. It is in a building that seems to have poor ventilation and air flow. The place has no air conditioning and the fans dotted around the place don't help at all. Da Nang city or who ever is responsible for this important museum needs to ensure that people are comfortable enough to stay and view the artefacts. The people working at the museum all looked hot and bothered. They weren't very friendly at all but I can understand working under these conditions!
